  "text": "It's very appealing to us. Thank you. Each of us gets the signals and dreams. I have been aware of plurality and communication, at least once waking up. Can you suggest a method whereby we might, shall I say, nullify the effect of the influence that we don't want from a negative source? I am Ra. There are various methods. We shall offer the most available or simple to share the difficult contact with the other selves associated with this working and to meditate in love for these cenders of images and light for self and other selves is the most available means of nullifying the effects of such occurrences to a down a grade these experiences by the use of intellect or the disciplines of will is to invite the prolonging of the effects. Far better than to share in trust such experiences and enjoin hearts and souls in love and light with compassion for the center and armor for the self.",
